name: Self-portrait 5
description: The project is about the problems with accept their body. I don’t know what to do. It’s grown a moustache. I don’t know what to do. Eyelid lift. What is eyelid surgery? I don’t know what to do. How to treat the pimples? I don’t know what to do. How to make small lips look bigger? The project is about contemporary social beauty stereotypes and the influence on the individuals. Whenever I look at my photos or videos of me, I'm so sad of myself. The project is about mother and daughter.
